Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You cooked all this yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, everything. Starting from the preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought you were going\Nto show me how you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.18,0:00:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right. As you can see,\NI'm in the middle of working!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're a novel author, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just shut up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I named that "Spring Pixie's Full Nudity Soup"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's amazingly tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you for that meal. It was tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a professional author,\Nso of course it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The feeling of wanting to cook a meal\Nfrom scratch for someone who's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I understand how\Nthe heroine thinks when she cooks for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I write novels as a hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But hobbies you don't seriously play\Nare all boring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because it's a hobby, I put all my might into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I like cooking even more thanks to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, this is from the neighbor, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The neighbor's home-cooked meal\Nis really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}The neighbor?\NWe don't get along at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So erotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No! Don't you have something else to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you only draw girls with small boobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if I give a request to make\Nthe heroine's boobs bigger, you ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm picky about the types of lewd art to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't want to draw anything\NI haven't seen in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-In real life...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(423.116,435.555)}Don't tell me that illustration from the other day was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.60,CenterSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(202.283,289.333)}When you speak \Nof dreams, you should laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Idiot! Lewd! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You definitely just imagined me\Ndoing really lewd things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I bought those string panties\Nso I can draw that lewd illustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're thinking I'm lewd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not to that extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,An older brother doesn't think of lewd things\Nwith his younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No matter how erotic you are,\Nit won't turn me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And moreover, I'd never make fun of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what an older brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't care about or trust any older brothers\Nwho are lewd liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, can that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that our neighbor, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"The neighbor? We don't get along at all."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.71,RightSignL2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz33.87\fs25\pos(753.367,152.334)}Yee-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.22,RightSignL2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz27.69\pos(189.8,184.333)}"The neighbor's home-cooked meal\Nis really delicious."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's true that I head over\Nto the neighbor's a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But there's a reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...something I can't say for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Always, all the time, everything is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't want to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'll prove that I'm not a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For the past year, I've been thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,about how I can get you\Nto recognize me as your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I finally get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll make my younger sister my heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll write a light-novel\Nthat's about my younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll write about my favorite thing in the world,\Nand create the ultimate light-novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not happy about that one bit!\NNot happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not going to open up my heart\Nwith anything like that! It's just gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hate older brothers who are liars!\NI don't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's do our best together next time, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my max-fire motivation, I'll do what I can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Several days passed. Before I knew it,\Nroughly two weeks were already gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't seen Sagiri's face ever since.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei, please do something about\Nthe proposal for your new title by this week.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'd like a little bit more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right. Then take your time to think it out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's really scary to turn down work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't publish a new title,\Nmy position disappears all too quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even the fans forget about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two years ago, I wrote and wrote,\Nyet not one book was published.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was losing heart,\Nand I'm about to be back in that state.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fighting such fears, but still, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wrote something interesting.\NI have a good feeling about this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's open?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Yamada Elf-sensei? Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I hope you don't mind my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right. Today was the promised day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait for me in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a serious look on her face...\NI've never seen it before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is my new novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.80,RightSignL2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(242.033,301.334)\frz2.804}Chronicles of\NWandering Cat Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.80,RightSignL2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz2.804\pos(236.733,387.556)}Yamada Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You said yesterday\Nthat you haven't written one word of it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With my ability "Summon Darkness",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I summoned a completed manuscript\Nfrom the demon realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-Impossible! Such an ability!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You thought I'd be surprised? You were\Ndesperately writing that until moments ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I totally wasn't writing.\NI totally summoned this from the demon realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you think I'm lying,\Nyou can check my laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You erased it just for a stupid little trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ya-Yamada Elf's new title...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B-But I'm Yamada Elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The manuscript is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Time for the showdown, Izumi Masamune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll see through your little piece\Nwith my God Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Yamada Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That novel you summoned\Nfrom the demon realm with all your might...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll have a read of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Interesting. It's tremendously interesting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The hand keeps flipping the pages.\NAnd my heart keeps wanting more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this the true skills of an author whose works\Nget turned into anime?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of that, all the heroines\Nhave small breasts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are so many poses that Eromanga Sensei\Nwould love to draw.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's full of situations and outfits\Nthat she might like!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's super erotic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's tuned to be ultra-specialized.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a light-novel made for Eromanga Sensei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is this manuscript for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, Masamune?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is very important. Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Of course, I'm dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't win against this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Was my manuscript that interestin—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No! That's not what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How dare you make me\Nread something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Such... Such...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Was it that boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The one I wrote will sell ten billion times more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't compete against this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This manuscript wasn't written\Nto amuse a lot of readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You put your soul into this,\Nand wrote this just for one person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Reading this crap of a manuscript\Nthat is definitely not sellable,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the only ones who would get emotional\Nin this whole world would be myself, and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,your younger sister, Eromanga Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-How'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious after reading this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's like you plainly wrote here\Nthat your younger sister is Eromanga Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was planning on having\Nmy younger sister read this novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think your thoughtfulness\Nwill get across to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This super-duper-ultra-passionate\N300 page love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was wondering what kind\Nof an exhibitionist you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But to think you weren't conscious of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I lost. I totally lost this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Such a lewd, amusing masterpiece...\NLost forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If it won't have those illustrations,\Nthen there's no point in leaving it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen, I've lost,\Nbut that doesn't mean you've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How are those different?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why you're so dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll win next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You won't say, "Nah, I'm not gonna\Nshow this to my younger sister," are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I was planning on it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you serious? If you fall, you'll get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eromanga-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri! I'm coming for you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, this is, um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri! I completed the manuscript\Nfor my new piece! I want you to read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's okay now. But, it's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Why did you do something so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because you never opened\Nthe door for me since that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The reason I didn't open my door for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Battle scenes. Have I gotten better\Nat drawing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's almost like someone else drew them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I watched videos of martial arts matches,\Nand read up on many references for weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's why it's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I don't like stories\Nwith people getting hurt or dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's from—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I've always been like that from before.\NDon't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's sad when the character you like\Nis no longer in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I've always resisted drawing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, seeing face-to-face for the first time,\Nand talking about creating titles...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I felt it wasn't right\Nfor me to just be good at drawing what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because I said you sucked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was really disappointed,\Nso I felt that I should fight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight, as in, against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No. Look at this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I color it, it looks like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is a version with a different hair style.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You learned how to draw\Ncharacters with big boobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I got it to a level where I can barely get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She looks like this when stripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think it's really erotic and very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So for the past couple weeks,\Nyou were practicing this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's impossible to drop me\Nfrom working on your new title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}What do you mean? Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I mean, you were hiding something from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}You were secretly meeting\Nwith our neighbor, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You seemed to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You'd never meet anyone like that\Noutside of your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since you started seeing her,\Nyou seemed really motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought, she must be your new illustrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I cooped myself up\Nin my room and practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-sensei said his younger sister\Nwas going to be his heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He said he was going to create\Nthe ultimate light-novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was actually happy about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and that's when I thought I had to draw\Nthe illustrations for it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm never, ever going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't hand over Izumi-sensei\Nto someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's all a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yamada-san next door is the popular author,\NYamada Elf-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yamada Elf-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. Sh-She's a huge fan of Eromanga Sensei,\Nand wants to work together with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So we engaged in a novel duel,\Nwith Eromanga-sensei at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? I didn't hear about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because I was afraid to be told you'd rather\Nwork with a popular author instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Impossible! Nii-san, you really are an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:17:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think so, too.\NI have to tell you in the end, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!\NThat's exactly how—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but, I've already defeated her.\NI won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's amazing.\NTo think you'd win against her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-sensei, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Actually, we were going to have you\Nread both and decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No need for that.\NFrom the start, I've already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's keep working together\Nfrom now on, Izumi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The pleasure is all mine, Eromanga-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I don't know anyone by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.23,RightSignL2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(537.817,233.444)\frz29.52}Untitled\NIzumi Masamune
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-R-R-Right. Y-Y-Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not flustered! No, not flustered one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be over there—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No good. I might die from shock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,U-U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think it's really interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't publish it as a book like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't have anyone else read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You're right. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right. That's how it should be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because we're siblings.\NI decided that I was going to be her family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with that stupid grin on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So? What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, Sagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have a dream now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right, a really big dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll turn this manuscript into a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's out of the question as is,\Nso I'll rethink it, and write a project proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll have my editor approve it, too.\NThat's where it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I'll make sure to turn this into a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll amuse tons of people with it, and have them\Nlove the main character and the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It'll get super popular, and make enough money\Nfor us to easily live on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And then, have it turn into an anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that your dream, Nii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no. That's all preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll buy a large LCD television\Nfor the living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and get ridiculously expensive speakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And then we'll have\Na magnificent cake, with candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll take you out of your room,\Nand we'll watch the anime together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It'll be our anime, where I wrote the story\Nand you drew the illustrations!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That way, I think both of us\Nwould have a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All the sad things will be blown away by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's my dream. It's the goal I have to get to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How is it? Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It won't help if I speak in a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. This time, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.49,0:22:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've always been like that, Izumi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You always give me dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's great, Izumi-sensei.\NLet's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you\Ndo something so fun all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's not a dream for you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's make that our dream, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right, right. I got it. Hold on for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our first step towards our dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think I'll ever forget about this day\Nfor the rest of my life.{\i0}
